\begin_layout Standard
正割函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\cot\theta$
\end_inset

 和余割函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\csc\theta$
\end_inset

 之间的关系:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\ensuremath{\cot\theta} & =\frac{\cos\theta}{\sin\theta}\\
\csc\theta & \ensuremath{=\frac{1}{\sin\theta}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

则两者之间有:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\cot^{2}\theta+1=\csc^{2}\theta
\]

\end_inset

这可以从三角函数的原始定义出发推导。由定义，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sin^{2}\theta+\cos^{2}\theta=1
\]

\end_inset

两边除以 
\begin_inset Formula $\sin^{2}\theta$
\end_inset

：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{\sin^{2}\theta}+\frac{\cos^{2}\theta}{\sin^{2}\theta}=\frac{1}{\sin^{2}\theta}
\]

\end_inset

即：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\csc^{2}\theta+\cot^{2}\theta=\csc^{2}\theta
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

