\begin_layout Standard
对于曲线
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}-y^{2}=1$
\end_inset

，它经过点
\begin_inset Formula $(1,0)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0},y_{0})=(x(\alpha),y(\alpha))$
\end_inset

