\begin_inset Formula $e^{x}$
\end_inset

 定义为满足 
\begin_inset Formula $y'=y$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $y(0)=1$
\end_inset

 的函数 
\begin_inset Formula $y(x)$
\end_inset

